{"tid":2190543,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"到底有幾多為一而一齊既情侶","createTime":"2020-09-05T18:13:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T22:46:35.000Z","uid":361169,"like":157,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"7d5664297e16e7ce4481ecde46c90a627bf96169","tid":2190543,"uid":361169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T18:13:08.000Z","msg":"人越大 見識既人越多<br />\n發現原來好多情侶為左一齊而一齊<br />\n<br />\n有啲人 因為對方有錢而一齊...<br />\n<br />\n有啲人拍左好耐拖 但其實並唔係咁愛<br />\n純粹係唔想自己一個人 而搵個人一齊<br />\n<br />\n有啲人同對方既價值觀明明唔夾 <br />\n但為左唔想失去對方 唔捨得 而勉強繼續一齊<br />\n<br />\n有啲人明知呢段關係係錯係冇結果<br />\n都要任性去開始 試過先知<br />\n<br />\n到底邊一種人最可悲"},{"pid":"2233ef40b439ff0e0f13c6c87a184058fe5bd103","tid":2190543,"uid":363977,"like":58,"dislike":1,"score":57,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T18:14:39.000Z","msg":"你後面個兩種都唔算為一齊而一齊喎"},{"pid":"c08e6426af146b9e4c64304edb04d0ee19f0edd8","tid":2190543,"uid":330457,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T18:15:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f41ad3a5cbe0cf34030af088006fd9b01cd6ab43","tid":2190543,"uid":374520,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T18:16:01.000Z","msg":"你覺得可悲唔代表當時人覺得可悲，最緊要知道自己想點"},{"pid":"598644c84e08efce025a316b875490166c8c3676","tid":2190543,"uid":77916,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"c08e6426af146b9e4c64304edb04d0ee19f0edd8","tid":2190543,"uid":330457,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T18:15:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T18:18:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a882aa651adbac46d94ab63d1c2fe24418298f81","tid":2190543,"uid":228308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c08e6426af146b9e4c64304edb04d0ee19f0edd8","tid":2190543,"uid":330457,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T18:15:28.000Z